<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>{وَلَيَنصُرَنَّ اللََّهُ مَن يَنصُرُهُ إِنَّ اللََّهَ لَقَوِيٌّ عَزِيزٌ <span class="c2">(٤٠)</span> الَّذِينَ إِن<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مَّكَّنَّاهُمْ فِي الْأَرْضِ أَقَامُوا الصَّلَاةَ وَآتَوُا الزَّكَاةَ وَأَمَرُوا بِالْمَعْرُوفِ وَنَهَوْا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>عَنِ الْمُنكَرِ وَلِلَّهِ عَاقِبَةُ الْأُمُورِ <span class="c2">(٤١)</span>}<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[الحج ٢٢: ٤٠ - ٤١]</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>